Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:03.28,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}And spikes may be sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:07.75,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}They want to see just the beautiful parts
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:11.14,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}Sitting in a shower of scarlet rain
